      "pos": "形容詞",
      "exampleEn": "Kasumi:\nYou know, you’re kind of revered by everyone else.\nBut to me, you’re just Elizabeth.\n\nElizabeth:\nGood. I’d hate to be revered by you.\nThat sounds exhausting.",
